{"tid":891811,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"另一半既前度","createTime":"2018-11-06T11:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T06:49:48.000Z","uid":140856,"like":9,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"63ea6b58f1240644107a6fa9ff7a81bb3c052628","tid":891811,"uid":140856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:50:43.000Z","msg":"寧願另一半<br />\n<br />\n正評 同過1個人拍拖5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n負評 同過4個人拍拖總共5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得同過一個人五年實在經歷太多野 去到邊都會諗起對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3933cd9002cf6b9aaf5b6f705c9c22bc9ca3567","tid":891811,"uid":140856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:17:45.000Z","msg":"五年... 真係好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792976f2975d8f1886b00f44924086a194cb0d3e","tid":891811,"uid":72690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T14:05:07.000Z","msg":"飛撚左佢囉"},{"pid":"c363b45d240909ac4a5603d60b2b7d1e56a480c4","tid":891811,"uid":190196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:58:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3a734c7add5dc8e2b0e5a5d92704ee9374c4159","tid":891811,"uid":140856,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c363b45d240909ac4a5603d60b2b7d1e56a480c4","tid":891811,"uid":190196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:58:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:31:28.000Z","msg":"好似佢地已經試過好多野 去過好多地方<br />\n點比都比唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71c6fd408f309615a9b2459eb0ff41ea0078b96","tid":891811,"uid":142329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:32:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99be6a2a49aa66f17c462096fef851cfec6025b8","tid":891811,"uid":116166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:36:52.000Z","msg":"我前度五年，現任五年"},{"pid":"a4d2a8ba0bfc30f67c37aaa0368f22ca426f75eb","tid":891811,"uid":112507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:17:24.000Z","msg":"咩都係假 愛你就夠啦<br />\n至少佢以後既回憶都係同你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同前度差唔多五年 <br />\n佢話唔愛 被分手 <br />\n我會覺得同佢有好多回億<br />\n但對佢嚟講 以前既野 don&rsquo;t give a shit <br />\n佢不知同現任幾happy <br />\n<br />\n所以唔洗灰心介意<br />\n佢中意你就得 而且佢更加唔會諗起"},{"pid":"01cbbcceaddc51af2b58e57b9d4ebfd18c87eff8","tid":891811,"uid":21187,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04774b5bd5be156fbf5265409ddfe796f901fb28","tid":891811,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63ea6b58f1240644107a6fa9ff7a81bb3c052628","tid":891811,"uid":140856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:50:43.000Z","msg":"寧願另一半<br />\n<br />\n正評 同過1個人拍拖5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n負評 同過4個人拍拖總共5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得同過一個人五年實在經歷太多野 去到邊都會諗起對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:01:01.000Z","msg":"同一人拍拖5年，佢隻西比同一人瘋狂抽插5年<br />\n<br />\n5年同4人拍拖，佢隻西比4條鳩瘋狂抽插5年"},{"pid":"b3f2cc2d2da9a02a3b1e8c5d0150c6cb50f2646f","tid":891811,"uid":175490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01cbbcceaddc51af2b58e57b9d4ebfd18c87eff8","tid":891811,"uid":21187,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:06:56.000Z","msg":"點解會咁..."},{"pid":"86cfbeb1439f4237d6d4d45baae1805ced5e6876","tid":891811,"uid":21187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3f2cc2d2da9a02a3b1e8c5d0150c6cb50f2646f","tid":891811,"uid":175490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01cbbcc